{
  "chapter": 32,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十二回 情海双姝\n\n凌风独自流浪至济宁，前往知府公馆探望苏蕙芷。蕙芷对他一往情深，邀他住下，两人月下饮酒，凌风醉中亲吻蕙芷眼睛。窗外，失明的阿兰偷看到这一幕，心碎离去，留下一封绝情信。次日凌风向蕙芷打听阿兰下落，蕙芷内心挣扎后告知阿兰昨夜已走。凌风急于追赶，蕙芷含泪送别，独自承受失恋之痛。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这可是知府公馆么？在下吴凌风请问苏蕙芷姑娘可在？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "管家",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "吴公子请进，小姐在厅上相待。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "text": "苏姑娘近来可好？我那捷弟本和我一起来看你，但在路上被一位老前辈叫去，他叫我代向你致意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "吴公子快请进屋，那日一别，我内心牵挂，日日盼您早来看我……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "吴相公，您是从淹水地方来的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "那黄河确是年年泛滥，治河的官儿，平日只知搜括民脂民膏，一旦大水临头，跑得比谁都快，这次大水，如果事先防范周详，总不至于如此，我义父为此事大为震怒，已上省城去请示了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "您先睡一会休息休息，等吃晚饭，我再来喊您。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "婢女",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "这是我们小姐住的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "text": "让你久等了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "吴相公，您礼仪真重，来咱们先喝酒。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "那日我见辛——辛相公喊您大哥，真是羡慕得很，我……我想，有一天我也能喊你大哥，那才好哩！",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "text": "我也很想有一个像你这样的妹子。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，真的么？你也别再叫我苏姑娘长、苏姑娘短的了，我妈叫我小蕙，你就这样叫我吧！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，你走了后，我真想念你，我天天算着日子，我知道你一定会来看我的，今早儿，我听喜鹊儿在树枝上呱呱地叫，我便知大哥会来了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "text": "小蕙妹子，我……我。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥你不用讲，我知道你也在想念我。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "我义父，他见我整天不乐，以为我生病了，大哥，我心里担忧，饭也吃不下，大哥，你不再离开我吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，我知道你不愿住在这儿，你要行侠江湖，难道我还会不愿跟着你吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "text": "妹子，你真好看。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "text": "妹子！",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，什么事？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "text": "我……我……想……亲亲你的眼睛……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "那阿兰姑娘，可是长得非常小巧标致吗？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "text": "小蕙妹子，阿兰正是像你讲的那模样，请你特别留心一点，她双目是瞎的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_bi_nv",
      "text": "你去叫阿兰姑娘来见吴相公吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "text": "妹子，你……你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_bi_nv",
      "text": "我是叫你去把小兰请来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fu",
      "text": "她是……什么……时候……时候走的？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "小芙",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "昨天晚上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fu",
      "text": "她为什么突然要走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "小芙",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "我也不知道，她临走时央求我递给吴相公一封信，那管家因他并非丫环使女，只是老太爷出巡时救回的孤女，所以也不能阻止，就让她走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fu",
      "text": "你快把那封信拿来。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，你可要好好保重。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凌风",
      "listener": "char_su_gu_niang",
      "text": "妹子，你待我好，我心里知道，待我追到阿兰，再来找你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    }
  ],
